### ShopFlow Microservices — HTTP Client
### IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client ile kullan

@product_url = http://localhost:8081
@customer_url = http://localhost:8082
@order_url = http://localhost:8083
@config_url = http://localhost:8888
@eureka_url = http://localhost:8761

# =====================================================
# CONFIG SERVER
# =====================================================

### Config Server Health
GET {{config_url}}/actuator/health

###

### Product Service Config
GET {{config_url}}/product-service/default

###

### Customer Service Config
GET {{config_url}}/customer-service/default

###

### Order Service Config
GET {{config_url}}/order-service/default

###

# =====================================================
# EUREKA SERVER
# =====================================================

### Eureka Health
GET {{eureka_url}}/actuator/health

###

### Kayıtlı Tüm Servisler
GET {{eureka_url}}/eureka/apps
Accept: application/json

###

# =====================================================
# PRODUCT SERVICE
# =====================================================

### Health Check
GET {{product_url}}/actuator/health

###

### Actuator — Tüm Endpoint'ler
GET {{product_url}}/actuator

###

### Actuator — JVM Memory
GET {{product_url}}/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used

###

### Tüm Ürünleri Getir
GET {{product_url}}/api/products

###

### Ürün Getir (ID ile)
GET {{product_url}}/api/products/1

###

### Stokta Olan Ürünleri Getir
GET {{product_url}}/api/products/available

###

### Ürün Ekle
POST {{product_url}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15",
  "description": "Apple akıllı telefon",
  "price": 45000,
  "stock": 10
}

###

### Ürün Ekle 2
POST {{product_url}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy S24",
  "description": "Android akıllı telefon",
  "price": 35000,
  "stock": 15
}

###

### Ürün Ekle 3
POST {{product_url}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MacBook Pro",
  "description": "Apple laptop",
  "price": 120000,
  "stock": 5
}

###

### Ürün Güncelle
PUT {{product_url}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "Apple akıllı telefon — güncel model",
  "price": 55000,
  "stock": 8
}

###

### Ürün Sil
DELETE {{product_url}}/api/products/1

###

### Stok Azalt
PUT {{product_url}}/api/products/1/decrease-stock?quantity=2

###

### Stok Artır
PUT {{product_url}}/api/products/1/increase-stock?quantity=2

###

### Toplu Ürün Getir (Batch)
POST {{product_url}}/api/products/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[1, 2, 3]

###

### Validation Hatası Testi — Fiyat negatif (400)
POST {{product_url}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -100,
  "stock": -5
}

###

### 404 Testi — Olmayan ürün
GET {{product_url}}/api/products/999

###

# =====================================================
# CUSTOMER SERVICE
# =====================================================

### Health Check
GET {{customer_url}}/actuator/health

###

### Tüm Müşterileri Getir
GET {{customer_url}}/api/customers

###

### Müşteri Getir (ID ile)
GET {{customer_url}}/api/customers/1

###

### Müşteri Ekle
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "email": "ahmet@example.com",
  "phone": "05551234567"
}

###

### Müşteri Ekle 2
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ayşe Kaya",
  "email": "ayse@example.com",
  "phone": "05559876543"
}

###

### Müşteri Ekle 3
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mehmet Demir",
  "email": "mehmet@example.com",
  "phone": "05553456789"
}

###

### Duplicate Email Testi — 409 Conflict
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kopya Kullanıcı",
  "email": "ahmet@example.com",
  "phone": "05550000000"
}

###

### Validation Hatası Testi — 400 Bad Request
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "gecersiz-email-formati"
}

###

### 404 Testi — Olmayan müşteri
GET {{customer_url}}/api/customers/999

###

# =====================================================
# ORDER SERVICE
# =====================================================

### Health Check
GET {{order_url}}/actuator/health

###

### Sipariş Oluştur — Tek Ürün
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sipariş Oluştur — Çok Ürün
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sipariş Oluştur — 2. Müşteri
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 2,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 3,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sipariş Getir (ID ile)
GET {{order_url}}/api/orders/1

###

### Müşterinin Tüm Siparişleri
GET {{order_url}}/api/orders/customer/1

###

### Müşteri Sipariş Özeti (Senaryo 1)
GET {{order_url}}/api/orders/customer/1/summary

###

### Sipariş Durumu Güncelle — CONFIRMED
PATCH {{order_url}}/api/orders/1/status?status=CONFIRMED

###

### Sipariş Durumu Güncelle — SHIPPED
PATCH {{order_url}}/api/orders/1/status?status=SHIPPED

###

### Sipariş Durumu Güncelle — DELIVERED
PATCH {{order_url}}/api/orders/1/status?status=DELIVERED

###

### Sipariş İptal Et — Stok İade (Senaryo 2)
DELETE {{order_url}}/api/orders/1

###

### Kargodaki Siparişi İptal Et — 400 hatası
DELETE {{order_url}}/api/orders/1

###

### Olmayan Sipariş — 404
GET {{order_url}}/api/orders/999

###

### ErrorDecoder Testi — Olmayan müşteri özeti — 404
GET {{order_url}}/api/orders/customer/999/summary

###

### Validation Testi — Boş items — 400
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": []
}

###

### Yetersiz Stok Testi — 400
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 9999
    }
  ]
}

###

# =====================================================
# SENARYO AKIŞI — Sırayla çalıştır
# =====================================================

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 1 — Ürün ekle
POST {{product_url}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Ürünü",
  "description": "Senaryo testi",
  "price": 100,
  "stock": 10
}

###

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 2 — Müşteri ekle
POST {{customer_url}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Müşteri",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "05550000001"
}

###

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 3 — Sipariş oluştur (stok: 10 → 8)
POST {{order_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "items": [{ "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }]
}

###

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 4 — Stok düştü mü kontrol et (8 olmalı)
GET {{product_url}}/api/products/1

###

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 5 — Siparişi iptal et (stok: 8 → 10)
DELETE {{order_url}}/api/orders/1

###

### [AKIŞ 1] Adım 6 — Stok geri geldi mi kontrol et (10 olmalı)
GET {{product_url}}/api/products/1

###
